BT /F2 22 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 740 Tm (AspieDad Communication Guide) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 720 Tm (A one-page summary for NT and Aspie family communication.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 684 Tm (What helps) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 664 Tm (- Be direct and specific about the real need.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 648 Tm (- Use one issue at a time instead of stacking problems.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 632 Tm (- Acknowledge feelings before moving to solutions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 616 Tm (- Allow processing time, but return to the issue.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 600 Tm (- Check understanding: "What did you hear me say?") Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 584 Tm (- Use concrete examples instead of broad accusations.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 568 Tm (- Make care visible with words, tone, and follow-up.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 532 Tm (What usually makes it worse) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 512 Tm (- Hinting and expecting mind-reading.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 496 Tm (- Raising too many issues in one conversation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 480 Tm (- Assuming bad motives too quickly.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 464 Tm (- Using "you always" and "you never.") Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 448 Tm (- Escalating volume, speed, or emotional intensity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 432 Tm (- Leading with logic alone when the other person needs acknowledgment.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 416 Tm (- Withdrawing without explanation or repair.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 380 Tm (Simple phrases that help) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 360 Tm (- "I want to understand what you mean.") Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 344 Tm (- "I need a few minutes to process, but I will come back.") Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 328 Tm (- "I know I may not have meant harm, but I can see this hurt.") Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 312 Tm (- "Do you want comfort, help, or just for me to listen?") Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 276 Tm (Core idea) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 256 Tm (Better communication is usually less about brilliance and more about clarity,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 84 240 Tm (timing, visible care, and a willingness to repair misunderstanding.) Tj ET
